    <string name="qbt_settings_help">Optional. Send torrents from a release to qBittorrent on your network. In qBittorrent: Tools → Preferences → Web UI. Enter the same address you use in a browser (e.g. http://192.168.1.5:8080) — do not add /api/v2. Leave username and password empty if Web UI authentication is disabled.</string>
