    <string name="rtorrent_section_title">rTorrent XML-RPC</string>
    <string name="rtorrent_settings_help">Optional. rTorrent is controlled over XML-RPC (often exposed as HTTP to an SCGI socket, e.g. nginx scgi_pass). Enter http://host:port or the full path to your RPC endpoint (e.g. …/RPC2). If the URL has no path, this app uses /RPC2. HTTP Basic auth if your proxy requires it. Reference: github.com/rakshasa/rtorrent</string>
