    <string name="deluge_section_title">Deluge Web UI</string>
    <string name="deluge_settings_help">Optional. Deluge Web UI JSON-RPC (same flow as github.com/jessielw/deluge-web-client). Enter the base URL you use in a browser (e.g. http://192.168.1.5:8112) — this app appends /json if needed. Web UI password only (daemon auth is separate). Ensure the Web UI can connect to your deluged host.</string>
